OL,5, Halifax has apologised for rejecting a 
OL,6, customer's mortgage application because
OL,7, the home owner is hosting two Ukrainian
OL,8, refugees.                              
OL,10,FDominik Zaum and his family have had a 
OL,11,Fmother and her young daughter staying  
OL,12,Fwith them in an annexe since June 2022.
OL,14,FWhen his mortgage came up for renewal, 
OL,15,Fhe applied for one with Halifax.       
OL,17,FBut Dominik was refused after Halifax  
OL,18,Fsaid there was a risk he could rent out
OL,19,Fthe space for commercial gain in the   
OL,20,Ffuture.                                
